attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Welcome to 654 E 7th St, a spacious 3 bed, 2 bath condo in South Boston’s desirable City Point. Built in 2018, this nearly 2,000 sq ft single-level home blends modern comfort with smart design. The open kitchen features a large island and dining area that flows into a sunlit living room with custom built-ins, a gas fireplace, and a sleek cocktail bar—perfect for entertaining. Step outside to a private deck, a great spot to relax or host guests. Oak hardwood floors run throughout, with two beautifully designed full baths featuring contemporary tile finishes. Central A/C and heat ensure year-round comfort. Includes two off-street parking spaces. Just a short walk to the beach, grocery stores, coffee shops, and Southie’s top restaurants—this is a perfect home for anyone looking to settle down and grow in one of Boston’s most vibrant neighborhoods.
